Sentencas: It was shown through a comprehensive impedance spectroscopy study that the impedance of the classic composite LSM:YSZ (lanthanum strontium manganite and yttria stabilized zirconia) solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) cathode can be described well with porous electrode theory.
Titulo: Impedance of SOFC electrodes: A review and a comprehensive case study on the impedance of LSM:YSZ cathodes

Sentencas: Furthermore, it was illustrated through a literature review on SOFC electrodes that porous electrode theory not only describes the classic LSM:YSZ SOFC cathode well, but SOFC electrodes in general.
Titulo: Impedance of SOFC electrodes: A review and a comprehensive case study on the impedance of LSM:YSZ cathodes

Sentencas: The extensive impedance spectroscopy study of LSM:YSZ cathodes consisted of measurements on cathodes with three different sintering temperatures and hence different microstructures and varying degrees of LSM/YSZ solid state interactions.
Titulo: Impedance of SOFC electrodes: A review and a comprehensive case study on the impedance of LSM:YSZ cathodes

Sentencas: LSM based composite cathodes, where YSZ was replaced with CGO was also studied in order to acquire further knowledge on the chemical compatibility between LSM and YSZ.
Titulo: Impedance of SOFC electrodes: A review and a comprehensive case study on the impedance of LSM:YSZ cathodes

Sentencas: All impedance measurements were acquired in the very broad temperature range of 200-900 degrees C for complete elucidation of the impedance.
Titulo: Impedance of SOFC electrodes: A review and a comprehensive case study on the impedance of LSM:YSZ cathodes

Sentencas: All impedance spectra were analyzed in terms of porous electrode theory.
Titulo: Impedance of SOFC electrodes: A review and a comprehensive case study on the impedance of LSM:YSZ cathodes

Sentencas: Physical materials parameters were extracted from the analysis, which were in excellent accordance with literature values.
Titulo: Impedance of SOFC electrodes: A review and a comprehensive case study on the impedance of LSM:YSZ cathodes

Sentencas: Valuable insight about the dissolution of Mn in the cathode composite material YSZ during preparation was furthermore provided along with valuable engineering characteristics such as the electrochemical utilization thickness.
Titulo: Impedance of SOFC electrodes: A review and a comprehensive case study on the impedance of LSM:YSZ cathodes

Sentencas: From the combined impedance study and literature review, it is clear, that porous electrode theory is the most suitable framework for any type of porous composite SOFC electrode evaluation.
Titulo: Impedance of SOFC electrodes: A review and a comprehensive case study on the impedance of LSM:YSZ cathodes
